<paragraph id="EA5E7314F24C9636C6988750FBECFAB8" blockId="22.[136,1452,616,1471]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C6988750FEFBFBEC" bold="true" box="[189,283,1120,1146]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Note:—</emphasis>
In the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="2DE10897F24C9636C7D98750FBB3FBED" authority=", Boissieu (1906)" authorityName=", Boissieu" authorityYear="1906" box="[508,1107,1120,1147]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Sanicula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="orthacantha" variety="brevispina">
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C7D98750FD0CFBEC" box="[508,748,1120,1146]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Sanicula orthacantha</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C5048750FC76FBEC" box="[801,918,1120,1146]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">brevispina</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="8E700EE5F24C9636C5868750FBB3FBED" author="Boissieu, H. de" box="[931,1107,1120,1147]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="418 - 437" refId="ref14286" refString="Boissieu, H. de (1906) Note sur quelques Ombelliferes de la Chine, d'apres les collections du Museum d'Histoire naturelle de Paris. Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France 53: 418 - 437. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00378941.1906.10831189" type="journal article" year="1906">Boissieu (1906)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
only cited the single collection 
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C6AD87B5FEA9FB08" box="[136,329,1156,1182]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">E.H. Wilson 7104</emphasis>
, which kept at BM, K and P respectively, and all well preserved and agree with the original description. As discussed by 
<bibRefCitation id="8E700EE5F24C9636C7678798FE14FB54" author="McNeill, J." box="[322,500,1192,1218]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="1112 - 1113" refId="ref14969" refString="McNeill, J. (2014) Holotype specimens and type citations: general issues. Taxon 63: 1112 - 1113. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / 635.7" type="journal article" year="2014">McNeill (2014)</bibRefCitation>
, these sheets all 
<typeStatus id="355ACDB6F24C9636C4888799FCEFFB55" box="[685,783,1193,1219]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">syntypes</typeStatus>
as 
<bibRefCitation id="8E700EE5F24C9636C5168798FC05FB55" author="Boissieu, H. de" box="[819,997,1192,1219]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="418 - 437" refId="ref14286" refString="Boissieu, H. de (1906) Note sur quelques Ombelliferes de la Chine, d'apres les collections du Museum d'Histoire naturelle de Paris. Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France 53: 418 - 437. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00378941.1906.10831189" type="journal article" year="1906">Boissieu (1906)</bibRefCitation>
did not designate a specimen as the type of 
<taxonomicName id="2DE10897F24C9636C68387FCFE17FB70" authorityName=", Boissieu" authorityYear="1906" box="[166,503,1228,1255]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Sanicula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="orthacantha" variety="brevispina">
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C68387FCFEABFB70" box="[166,331,1228,1254]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">S. orthacantha</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C7A787FCFE17FB70" box="[386,503,1228,1254]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">brevispina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. According to ICN Art. 9.17 (
<bibRefCitation id="8E700EE5F24C9636C56087FCFBC1FB70" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[837,1057,1228,1254]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refId="ref15213" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code). Regnum Vegetabile 159. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten, 254 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="D895AF06F24C9636C58387FDFC3EFB70" box="[934,990,1228,1254]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation id="8E700EE5F24C9636C21187FCFB09FB70" author="Pimenov, M. G." box="[1076,1257,1228,1254]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="106 - 239" refId="ref15038" refString="Pimenov, M. G. (2017) Updated checklist of Chinese Umbelliferae: Nomenclature, Synonymy, Typification, Distribution. Turczaninowia 20: 106 - 239. https: // doi. org / 10.14258 / turczaninowia. 20.2.9" type="journal article" year="2017">Pimenov (2017)</bibRefCitation>
listed the P sheet as 
<typeStatus id="355ACDB6F24C9636C68087C0FEE7FA9C" box="[165,263,1264,1290]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">holotype</typeStatus>
of this variety is an error to be corrected to 
<typeStatus id="355ACDB6F24C9636C4C087C0FCACFA9C" box="[741,844,1264,1290]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">lectotype</typeStatus>
(McNeil 2014). Therefore, the P (barcode P03226637) sheet should be cited as 
<typeStatus id="355ACDB6F24C9636C7B28624FDE1FAB8" box="[407,513,1300,1326]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">lectotype</typeStatus>
, and the sheets at BM and K are isolectotypes.
</paragraph>
